metadata.name: Grandma
metadata.description:
Title: Grandma

Creator: RockofAJs

Edition: 1/1

Date: 2022

Poetry: Grandma as strong as can be  
As children they are the ones we always want to see

The same as our mothers but different indeed 
The grandmother brings a softness we need

Don't take her for granted or you’ll see her might 
Because Grandma’s are strong and never back away from a fight
